---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use | The Açai Club" description="Terms & conditions for using The Açai Club website & services.">

  <section class="pt-28 pb-24 bg-dark min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">

      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-4">
        Terms of Use
      </h1>
      <p class="text-grey text-sm mb-12">Last updated: 6 May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-8 text-grey leading-relaxed">

        <p>
          These Terms of Use govern your use of theacaiclub.com & our associated ordering platform at order.theacaiclub.com. By using our site, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please stop using our site immediately.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            The Açai Club is operated by THE ACAI CLUB, with a registered address at 10a High Street, Datchet, United Kingdom SL3 9EA. Our online ordering platform is provided by EPoS Technologies Limited (Company No. 07122283), 11 Wharf Road, Enfield, EN3 4TA, United Kingdom.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">2. Use of This Website</h2>
          <p>You may use our website for lawful purposes only. You must not:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Use the site in any way that breaches applicable law or regulation</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of our site or systems</li>
            <li>Introduce viruses, malware, or other harmful material</li>
            <li>Reproduce or redistribute content without our express written permission</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">3. Orders & Payment</h2>
          <p>
            All online orders are processed through order.theacaiclub.com. By placing an order, you confirm that the information you provide is accurate & complete.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Payments are processed securely by Stripe. Once an order is confirmed & payment taken, you will not be able to cancel your order. To amend or cancel, please contact your nearest store directly as soon as possible.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Prices displayed are subject to change. We will inform you of any pricing errors before processing your order.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">4. Refunds</h2>
          <p>
            If you believe an item does not meet the description or is of unsatisfactory quality, please contact us. We may request a photograph of the issue. Refunds for online orders will be returned to your original payment method within 5–7 business days. Cash orders must be resolved in-store.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">5. Food Allergies</h2>
          <p>
            Our products are prepared in an open kitchen where allergens are handled. While we take precautions, we cannot guarantee that any product is free from allergens due to shared equipment & preparation areas.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you have a serious allergy or intolerance, please contact your nearest store directly before placing an order. See our <a href="/allergens/" class="text-charcoal hover:text-light transition-colors">Allergens page</a> for more information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this website, including text, images, logos & design, is the property of The Açai Club or its licensors. You may not reproduce, distribute, or commercially exploit any content without our express written permission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, The Açai Club accepts no liability for any loss or damage arising from your use of this website or reliance on any content published here. We make no guarantee that the site will always be available or free from errors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">8. Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Use of our website is also governed by our <a href="/privacy/" class="text-charcoal hover:text-light transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by the laws of England & Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England & Wales.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 space-y-1">
            <p>The Açai Club</p>
            <p>10a High Street, Datchet, United Kingdom SL3 9EA</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@theacaiclub.com" class="text-charcoal hover:text-light transition-colors">hello@theacaiclub.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
